# API layer

- All HTTP via `src/services/api.ts` (`fetchApi<T>`).
- Types in `src/types/` use `readonly`; map JSON in services, not in JSX.
- Hooks (`useReleases`, `useInfrastructure`) expose `{ data, error, isLoading }`.
- Mock data lives in `public/api/` until `VITE_API_BASE` points to a real backend.
